As seen with altered plasma protein mixture Idea-ATIII showed also high-affinity binding to gp120 (Fig. 6E), to CD4 (Fig. 6F) and to the PDI (Fig. 6G). Reliable on and off rates and dissociation rate constants kd [s
−1
] can not be given, as the KD is dependent on both the association (on) and dissociation (off) rates of the compound and the off-rates were too slow to be meaningfully determined.
